{"tid":1065453,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搞百大最美臉孔有咩意義","createTime":"2019-03-17T09:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T10:11:59.000Z","uid":232334,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7356c422a384804ee4124d37bf6a9572f87da60d","tid":1065453,"uid":232334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T09:17:47.000Z","msg":"想知外國成日搞埋曬啲乜野百大最美臉孔<br />\n一年有成2-3個乜乜百大最美臉孔 其實有咩意義<br />\n年年都係果幾條友上榜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且又吾知根據咩標準黎排位<br />\n好似 周子瑜獲獲都上榜 年年頭10名都有佢份 亞洲最美臉孔=周子瑜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑人白人 乜野種族人都混埋一齊黎排 個人覺得好無謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似用黎造新聞 繼續抬舉已經紅左既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">美國知名電影評論網站TC Candler公布了2018年亞太區最美臉孔100人排行榜，該評選除了由外表進行評選，並會以文化背景、生活模式、公眾意見等多方面，選出亞太區百大最美臉孔。而去年封全球最美亞軍的韓國女團「TWICE」台灣成員周子瑜就屈居第四，第三名則是參加大陸節目《創造101》的大陸女星楊超越；第二名是日本人氣女星石原聰美，韓國女團BLACK PINK的泰國成員Lisa就登上冠軍寶座。</span>"},{"pid":"c5e25ba4413251d01aa2c124d1563fcda35fc88e","tid":1065453,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T09:20:17.000Z","msg":"富豪揀女用"},{"pid":"2fffd22fe733bf6ff049f9d8e94b1960a6b43bee","tid":1065453,"uid":78885,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T09:21:29.000Z","msg":"周子瑜真心靚喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3097a4d0647b9230d0dc7e7d29bdfbc8bea8849","tid":1065453,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T09:23:34.000Z","msg":"邊個hit咪邊個上榜囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完笑下咪算囉，咁認真做乜"},{"pid":"da2c2dae6e0f5494d64457ad385f6d60f31ce05b","tid":1065453,"uid":123121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"